Title: DKNY Delicious Night EDP - 100 ml
Description: Purple velvet - sensual and tempting - a scent of passion. DKNY Delicious Night beguiles with its mysteriously dark aroma. Images of subterraneous darkness, a screen of smoky purple haze swirls around your senses. Recklessly feminine, a single whiff of this heady Eau de Perfume makes you pulsate with tangible energy. The fashion house of Donna Karan New York seeks inspiration in the intoxicating nights of vibrant New York City for Delicious Night. Opening with a tantalising top note of frosty pomelo, ginger and luscious blackberry, Delicious Night mingles spontaneously with pink freesia and dry, effervescent martini. The aroma trails into a sophisticated heart note of glimmering night orchid, jasmine and a hint of luscious pink iris. The ambrosial base of frankincense, myrrh, vetiver and spicy patchouli achieve a vividly brazen, sensual essence that is certainly unforgettable. The uniquely concocted Delicious Night is pertinently packaged in a perfectly spherical apple-shaped globe, reminiscent of the forbidden fruit and a metaphor for the tempting indulgence of the Big Apple. The incandescent purple of Delicious Night envelops you in its powerful, urbane aroma - haunting like the moonlight and provocatively undeniable.
